      "text": "みなさん、そろそろライブも終盤ですが\nここでサプライズゲストをお呼びします",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Everyone‚ we're nearing the end of the live show‚\nbut we have a surprise guest for you.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 4.1333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_yamagatastage-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 6.5333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_06_04/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_06_04-yu001.m4a",
      "text": "ピアニストでもある、すみれちゃんのお兄さんです\nどうぞ拍手でお迎え下さい！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "He's Sumire-chan's brother‚ who's also a pianist.\nPlease give him a warm welcome with your applause!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 10.3666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_yamagatastage-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 12.9666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_06_04/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_06_04-smr001.m4a",
      "text": "お兄ちゃん、かもーん！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Big brother‚ come on!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 12.9666666667,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_clap-03.m4a",
