      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 15.6333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "すみれの兄",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire’s",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_06_04/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_06_04-smrbro001.m4a",
      "text": "ど、どうも……みなさん、すみれがいつもお世話に……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "W-Well… everyone‚ thank you for always taking care of Sumire…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 16.7333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_yamagatastage-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 27.3666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_06_04/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_06_04-smr002.m4a",
      "text": "お兄ちゃん、もっと堂々として！\nみんな、この人が私の大好きなお兄ちゃんです！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Big brother‚ be more confident!\nEveryone‚ this is my beloved brother!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 27.3666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "すみれの兄",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire’s",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_06_04/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_06_04-smrbro002.m4a",
      "text": "こ、こんな所で大好きとか言うなよ……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "D-Don't say you love me in a place like this…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 32.4,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_yamagatastage-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 36.0333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_06_04/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_06_04-smr003.m4a",
      "text": "えーっ？　兄妹が仲良くて何が悪いの？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Eh~? What's wrong with siblings being close?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 36.0333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_yamagatastage-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 40.5666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_06_04/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_06_04-yu002.m4a",
      "text": "すみれちゃん、めっちゃブラコンや\nでも、そんなとこも可愛いなぁ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Sumire-chan‚ you're such a brocon.\nBut that's also cute.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 43.2333333334,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_yamagatastage-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 46.1
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_06_04/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_06_04-rui002.m4a",
      "text": "ふふっ、仲が良くて結構ね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Fufu‚ it's nice that you're close.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 46.1,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_yamagatastage-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 49.4
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_06_04/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_06_04-rui003.m4a",
      "text": "では、この街とトリエルを繋ぐ二人のセッションを\nみなさん、聴いて下さい",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Then‚ everyone‚ please listen to\na session that connects this town and TRINITYAiLE.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 53.2,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-in-single-02.m4a",
          "delay": 5033.3333333,
          "startTime": 58.2333333333
        },
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_cheers-in-01.m4a",
          "delay": 1766.6666666999972,
          "startTime": 54.9666666667
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_yamagatastage-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
