      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_06_04/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_06_04-smr004.m4a",
      "text": "じゃあ、お兄ちゃん",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Okay‚ big brother.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 60.7,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "すみれの兄",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire’s",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_06_04/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_06_04-smrbro003.m4a",
      "text": "あ、うん、じゃあ――",
      "translations": {
        "en": "O-Oh‚ okay‚ then――",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 62.7666666667,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-in-single-02.m4a",
          "delay": 1466.6666665999983,
          "startTime": 64.2333333333
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_yamagatastage-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 67.5666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_yamagatastage-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 77.2666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_06_04/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_06_04-smr005.m4a",
      "text": "（トリエルのファンのみんなも聴き惚れてる……）\n（お兄ちゃんのピアノは、やっぱり世界一だよ）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "(All the TRINITYAiLE fans are mesmerized…)\n(My brother's piano playing is the best in the world.)",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 82.6,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_06_04/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_06_04-smr006.m4a",
      "text": "（やっぱりお兄ちゃんはピアノを諦めちゃダメ）\n（こんなに沢山の人が認めてくれてるんだもん）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "(He shouldn't give up on piano.)\n(So many people acknowledge him.)",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 92.2333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_yamagatastage-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 97.2333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_06_04/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_06_04-smr007.m4a",
      "text": "（私も、諦めない）\n（自分の夢も、酒造も、そしてお兄ちゃんの夢も）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "(I won't give up either.)\n(My dream‚ the brewery‚ and my brother's dream too.)",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 100.1333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_yamagatastage-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 106.4
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_06_04/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_06_04-smr008.m4a",
      "text": "（私も瑠依ちゃんみたいに強く生きる）\n（欲しいもの、全部手に入れるんだ）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "(I'll live strong like Rui-chan.)\n(I'll get everything I want.)",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 110.7666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_yamagatastage-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 115.2666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_06_04/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_06_04-smr009.m4a",
      "text": "（――だから、もう何があっても、絶対に諦めない）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "(――So‚ no matter what happens‚ I'll never give up.)",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 115.7333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_yamagatavenue-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s2",
      "startTime": 122.2666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_yamagatavenue-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s2",
      "startTime": 122.2666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_06_04/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_06_04-yu003.m4a",
      "text": "見てみい、瑠依ちゃん\nお客さん、めっちゃ盛り上がってるな",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Look‚ Rui-chan.\nThe audience is so hyped up.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 124.9333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_yamagatavenue-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s2",
      "startTime": 127.9
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_06_04/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_06_04-rui004.m4a",
      "text": "ええ、驚いたわ\nリハの時より、数段いいわね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yeah‚ I'm surprised.\nThey're several levels better than during rehearsal.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 130.3333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_yamagatavenue-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s2",
      "startTime": 132.6333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_06_04/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_06_04-yu004.m4a",
      "text": "これはうちらも、うかうかしとったら\n置いてかれてしまうかもしれんなぁ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "At this rate‚ if we slack off‚\nwe might get left behind.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 135,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_yamagatavenue-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s2",
      "startTime": 137.6333333333
    },
