      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire’s",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_06_04/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_06_04-smrmom001.m4a",
      "text": "一年先まであるじゃないの……！\nこんなに沢山……？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "There are orders for a year ahead…!\nSo many…?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 262.9666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "すみれの父",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire’s",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_06_04/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_06_04-smrdad001.m4a",
      "text": "……まさか、俺が退院してきたら\nこんなことになってるとはな……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…I never thought things would turn out like this\nafter I was discharged…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 268.7,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_okuyamaliving-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s3",
      "startTime": 271.5333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_06_04/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_06_04-yu011.m4a",
      "text": "今後も町おこしイベントは継続予定やし\nまだまだ増えると思います",
      "translations": {
        "en": "We're planning to continue holding town revitalization events‚\nso I think the orders will keep increasing.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 274.8666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_okuyamaliving-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s3",
      "startTime": 277.5333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_06_04/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_06_04-rui013.m4a",
      "text": "お父様も快方に向かってるとお聞きしました\n良かったです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I heard you're recovering well‚ sir.\nI'm glad to hear that.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 280.8666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_okuyamaliving-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s3",
      "startTime": 282.3
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "すみれの母",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire’s",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_06_04/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_06_04-smrmom002.m4a",
      "text": "ありがとうございます\nお二人にはなんとお礼を言ったらいいのか",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Thank you so much.\nWe don't know how to thank you enough.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 284.9,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_okuyamaliving-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s3",
      "startTime": 288.9
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "すみれの父",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire’s",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_06_04/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_06_04-smrdad002.m4a",
      "text": "ああ、すみれはいい友達をもったな\n俺は、それが分かったのが一番嬉しいよ……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ah‚ you've made good friends‚ Sumire.\nThat's what makes me the happiest…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 293.6333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_okuyamaliving-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s3",
      "startTime": 298.3333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
