      "text": "お兄ちゃん、これでうちも人を雇えるし\nお金にも余裕が出来るよね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Big brother‚ now we can hire people\nand have more financial leeway‚ right?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 302,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "すみれの兄",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire’s",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_06_04/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_06_04-smrbro004.m4a",
      "text": "ああ、そうだな。凄いよ、すみれ達は",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ah‚ you're right. It's amazing‚ what Sumire has done.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 304.3333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_okuyamaliving-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s3",
      "startTime": 310.6666666667
    },
    {
